Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please fondle them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.05,TS02,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}11th of September
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen my treasure yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.40,0:02:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I highly recommend the girl with glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There's also a picture of her without glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think she looks sexy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She turns into a complete hottie whenever she takes off her glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God this is so hot! She's Captain Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why am I doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a boy's love book in my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really {\i1}are{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you closing the door on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go or I'm going to call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a true pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to pass me off as an intruder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it has come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! I'm going to be kidnapped and imprisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want? Do you want to speak with Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't have any business with her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you sure live in a nice house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your room has a nice atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard something I can't let pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... When I think about how fluffy your bed is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell do you know how comfortable my bed is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here today because I have something to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.00,TS02,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}10th of September
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what is it-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable... How dare you look at me while I take a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My glasses, which have a refractive index of 1.60,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a super water-repellent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,multi-coated spherical surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,visible-light transmittance of around 12-35%,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a celluloid frame that guards against 99.9% of all UV rays!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those look like really valuable paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would Subaru-sama like a scone set?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come here just to leisurely drink tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the photos you took earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, these aren't good enough to sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You intended to sell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had an Overlooking Party meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't earn some cash now, I won't... I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have enough cash to make and publish my own doujinshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is troublesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ojou-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard your story over the phone with Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please scold her as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you had let me know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ojou-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Subaru, it's only a few pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in return, I want you to stop abusing my butler with your photo shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's within my power, I will fulfill your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now! No pushing, no pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there, I want this picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, my plan is coming along perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in a slump and I couldn't get more than half of it done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this an entire volume, Narunaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too thick. The stapler won't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you wait until you finish the volume before you sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have fans who are waiting for my new book!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I have a fan club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, honestly, it's a bit embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even their greeting has my name in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their greeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three! Two! One!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakuru, Nakuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if we aren't able to finish this by tomorrow, the plan for the whole event will be be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three! Two! One!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakuru, Nakuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, why am I even doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the one who flew in when I said I would pay you for your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show my gratitude to Kureha-chan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean these photos of Konoe-senpai are payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very precious off-shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're great, Narunaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would do anything to get my hands on these!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else I can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're offering...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in! My brother's not home because he's at Kurase-senpai's house today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who's the Seme and who's the Uke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's my first time in a boy's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of a real boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waste bin of a real boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real boy's porn magazines!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Idiot-Chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that even he has an interest in women.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triangle Love! This'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give him this magazine as thanks for letting me have a look inside his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm out of ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up! How many do we need to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to borrow your shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, then I'll get you a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate we won't be ready by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I call for more help?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Su-Subaru-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Suzutsuki Kanade as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked them for a little help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Konoe-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you. You finished it on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I even finished the volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the entire volume?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to write the continuation very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're going to head home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Wait, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still have something for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I want to ask Subaru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I have something I'm confused about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:11:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about BL novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about BL...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about glasses either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not about glasses either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Then what are you worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not being frank!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Please wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.16,TS03,,0000,0000,0000,,A shocking truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wild Narunaru appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.03,TS03,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The likes of which have never been seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.45,TS03,,0000,0000,0000,,The real criminal's confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'll figure something out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stop halfway through when you're trying to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning is just a few hours away, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best for tomorrow's exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good at writing fiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jirou... I've always been in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.90,TS02,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}11th of September
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your purchase!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we dressed like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disguises are fundamental to stalking, Usami-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to blend in with the crowd to deceive our target.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't quite sound right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Narunaru's worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't even tell us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be of some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all sold out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
