Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BL novels...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She brought it up! What the hell do you plan to do to me this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't concentrate on my writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think when you see my chest?
