Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, there was an incident a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone confessed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A confession?! Not a complaint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a boy! My classmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's someone who I don't talk to much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But suddenly he said that he loved me and that he wanted me to go out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. So what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rejected him, of course.
