Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decided what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had decided to give all of my high school life to BL novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what does that have to do with your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly speaking, I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why he confessed to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm not one to say it, but I am not the type who is very popular among boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I wondered several things about myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
