Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please fondle my breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHY?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a rumor!
