Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, why do I have to fondle your breasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a complex about my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like for them to be smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, everyone has one or two complexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also have something that doesn't seem like it can be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overall, males like to drool over big breasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they won't fall in love with you for your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please prove with your body that boys don't fall in love with our breasts!
