Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you for advice because I thought you could help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would be able to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I bear through this,
